text: ao krom robsakhnhom. nih kuchea satv audth nhi robsa a l laoh del chea ph st tang muoy samreab puok anak . dau che neah chaur puok anak touk aoy vea daer sai now leu dei robsa a l laoh choh haey puok anak kom bahpeal vea daoy brakear akrak namuoy aoy saoh . baemindauchnaohte tearounakamm nung thleak mk leu puok anak chab nih cheaminkhan
